    ax.annotate(f'{height:.2f}', (p.get_x() + p.get_width() / 2, height),

- Tá»« báº£ng káº¿t quáº£ nÃ y (hÃ¬nh bÃªn dÆ°á»›i), báº¡n convert long to wide Ä‘á»ƒ count yes náº±m á»Ÿ 1 cá»™t vÃ  count no náº±m á»Ÿ 1 cá»™t.
- Sau Ä‘Ã³ báº¡n táº¡o cá»™t percent lÃ  káº¿t quáº£ tÃ­nh toÃ¡n dá»±a trÃªn 2 cá»™t count yes vÃ  count no', 'created_at': '2024-04-13 04:16:02', 'author': 799663797270872095}, {'id': 1228558743885840468, 'content': 'Má»¥c tiÃªu cá»§a mÃ¬nh lÃ  muá»‘n tÃ­nh % yes, no trong cÃ¹ng 1 job', 'created_at': '2024-04-13 04:13:50', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228558241403895878, 'content': 'Cá»™t count cá»§a mÃ¬nh sá»‘ khÃ¡c mÃ  nhá»‰', 'created_at': '2024-04-13 04:11:50', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228557185194135633, 'content': 'MÃ¬nh váº«n chÆ°a hiá»ƒu cÃ¡ch lÃ m láº¯m', 'created_at': '2024-04-13 04:07:38', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228556885158789243, 'content': 'káº¿t quáº£ nhÆ° tháº¿ nÃ y lÃ  Ä‘Ãºng nhÃ© báº¡n, giá» chá»‰ cáº§n tÃ­nh percent lÃ  Ä‘Æ°á»£c áº¡', 'created_at': '2024-04-13 04:06:26', 'author': 799663797270872095}, {'id': 1228377872750874756, 'content': 'Cá»™t count cá»§a mÃ¬nh giÃ¡ trá»‹ khÃ¡c Ã¡', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 16:15:07', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228377513827242074, 'content': 'nhÆ°ng táº¡i sao cá»™t percent ra 50.0 v báº¡n nhá»', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 16:13:41', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228377046426587277, 'content': 'okee mÃ¬nh thá»­ liá»n nhen', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 16:11:50', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228375625774010388, 'content': "```job_data = train_df.groupby(['job', 'y']).agg({'y': 'count'}).rename(columns={'y': 'count'}).reset_index()
job_data = calculate_percentage_yes_no(job_data)
print(job_data)```", 'created_at': '2024-04-12 16:06:11', 'author': 1091998511060488303}, {'id': 1228375582060839083, 'content': "Hi báº¡n, Ä‘Ã¢y lÃ  cÃ¡ch viáº¿t cá»§a mÃ¬nh nha, báº¡n cÃ³ thá»ƒ thá»­
```def calculate_percentage_yes_no(job_data):
    # Group the data by job and y
    grouped = job_data.groupby(['job', 'y']).agg({'y': 'count'}).rename(columns={'y': 'count'}).reset_index()
    # Calculate the total count for each job category
    grouped['total'] = grouped.groupby('job')['count'].transform('sum')
    # Calculate the percentage of 'yes' and 'no' for each job category
    grouped['percentage'] = (grouped['count'] / grouped['total']).mul(100).round(2)
    # Select the relevant columns
    grouped = grouped[['job', 'y', 'count', 'percentage']]
    return grouped```", 'created_at': '2024-04-12 16:06:00', 'author': 1091998511060488303}, {'id': 1228372049777397801, 'content': 'Ngay chá»— nÃ y nhen', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:51:58', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228372039992217620, 'content': None, 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:51:56', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228371799977230336, 'content': 'ÄÃ¢y áº¡', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:50:59', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228371791152677044, 'content': 'https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1jlO1BUAWYg3fZZVHlbu1fT-yvNR0fu5M', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:50:57', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228371594267853021, 'content': 'Váº­y báº¡n cho mÃ¬nh xin link colab cá»§a báº¡n nha', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:50:10', 'author': 1091998511060488303}, {'id': 1228370535801553027, 'content': 'MÃ¬nh Ä‘ang lÃ m vá»›i python áº¡', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:45:57', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228370270474207273, 'content': 'dáº¡ mÃ  báº¡n Ä‘ang lÃ m vá»›i SQL hay vá»›i Python Ä‘Ã³ áº¡', 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:44:54', 'author': 1091998511060488303}, {'id': 1228369856097681541, 'content': None, 'created_at': '2024-04-12 15:43:15', 'author': 1124561460157239376}, {'id': 1228369352135282688, 'content': "total= count('yes)+ count(no)
